<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>jīn yè xīng guāng càn làn 迦南1276</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 jīn yè xīng guāng càn làn jīn yè qún xīng wú mián
 jīn yè gē shēng xiǎng biàn sì fāng jīn yè qí dǎo bù duàn
 jīn yè zhǔ ēn pèi jiàng zǔ guó de dà hǎo hé shān
 jīn yè yǔ zhǔ qīng xīn jiāo tán shén zhōu yào xiàng shén yǎng liǎn</lyrics>
</song>